	<description><![CDATA[<b>Art Table Lite</b> is used to create sortable, searchable, paginated tables from an SQL Query. It contains a limited set of functionality from our popular Art Table full extension. © <a href=http://www.artetics.com>Artetics.com</a> - Where art meets aesthetics.<link href=../modules/mod_arttable/library/uikit/css/uikit.almost-flat.min.css rel=stylesheet><script src=../modules/mod_arttable/library/uikit/js/uikit.min.js></script><hr><div class=uk-grid><div class=uk-width-medium-1-2><div><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/art-table-lite-logo-600-ls.jpg style=max-width:40px> <span style=font-size:24px;position:relative;top:5px>Art Table Lite</span></div></div></div><hr><p>Art Table Lite is a free module. Artetics.com provides limited support for free products. However we do provide some resources to make seeking help with free products easy. 'Discussions' below is our support forum. 'Knowledgebase' is our documentation. 'Premium Support' is for purchasing support time for feature requests or custom modifications. 'Contact Us' is to send our team an email.<p>We hope you enjoy Art Table Lite!<div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box uk-margin"><div class="uk-grid uk-width-1-1"data-uk-grid-margin=""><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4 uk-row-first"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_easydiscuss&view=index&Itemid=902&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTable_Full_Version_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target=_blank>Discussions</a></div><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/support/knowledgebase?utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTable_Full_Version_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target=_blank>Knowledgebase</a></div><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&view=product&layout=show&Itemid=903&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTable_Full_Version_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target=_blank>Premium Support</a></div><div class="uk-text-center uk-width-medium-1-4"><a href="http://www.artetics.com/contact-us?utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTable_Full_Version_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-large"target=_blank>Contact Us</a></div></div></div><h2>Check out how Art Table Lite stacks up against the full version!</h2><table class="uk-table uk-table-condensed uk-table-striped"><thead><tr><th class=uk-width-1-3 colspan=2><th class="uk-text-center uk-width-1-3"><div style=font-size:22px;line-height:28px>Lite Version</div><th class="uk-text-center uk-width-1-3"><div style=font-size:22px;line-height:28px>Full Version</div><tbody style=font-size:14px!important><tr><td colspan=6><div style=font-size:22px;line-height:28px lcass=uk-margin>Features</div><tr><td>Load jQuery library<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Load jQuery javascript library in your page. Choose no to not load jQuery from Art Table."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Create Table from SQL Query<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Enter an SQL Query here and Art Table will run your query and transform your data into a sortable and searchable table."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Multiple Database Types<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Select data from a variety of database types including MySQL, MySQLi, MSSQL, Sqlite, PostgreSQL, FBSQL, Gladius, MaxDB, MSQL, MSSQLPO, MySQLt, ODBC, and Sybase. "><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Change Table Type<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="There are 4 types of tables that can be used and one chart type which can be used to create charts such as line graphs, bar charts and more. The most popular choice for table creation seems to be the Table Sorter. Other choices here include Table Sorter, Sortable, Data Table, HTML Table and Chart."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>25 Table Themes<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Choose from one of many themes to change the look of your table. The most popular choice amongst users is ui-lightness theme. Other choices include black-tie, blitzer, cupertino, dark-hive, dot-luv, eggplant, excite-bike, flick, hot-sneaks, humanity, le-frog, mint-choc, overcast, pepper-grinder, redmond, smoothness, south-street, start, sunny, swanky-purse, trontastic, ui-darkness, ui-lightness and vader."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Change Table/Chart Data Source<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="This is the data source type for the data you want to load into a table or chart. Choices here include HTML Table, SQL Query and CSV File."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Create Table from HTML Table<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Only use this if you have set your Table Source to HTML Table. Enter your raw html and Art Table will transform your plain, basic HTML table into a sortable and searchable table."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Create Table from CSV File<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Load table from data held in a CSV File. Provide the file path to your CSV file in your server file system."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Create 5 Different Charts<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Chart types include LineChart, AreaChart, BarChart, ColumnChart and PieChart."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Convert Links and Images<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Toggle between automatically (standard link and image conversion), by pattern (follows the pattern set in Link Conversion Pattern parameter) and no which doesn't convert links and images. The way this works is if your data contains a path to an image or a URL then Art Table will make the image display using HTML img tag or in the case of a URL it will transform the URL into a clickable link."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td>Generate Excel File<td class=uk-text-right><span data-uk-tooltip=""title="Indicate excel file name only if you need to generate an Excel file from your SQL query."><i class=uk-icon-info-circle></i></span><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-lock style=color:#ed037c></i><td class=uk-text-center><i class=uk-icon-check style=color:#6ec409></i><tr><td colspan=2><h3 class=uk-margin>Price</h3><td class=uk-text-center><h3 class=uk-margin>$0</h3><td class=uk-text-center><h3 class=uk-margin>$20.00</h3><tr><td colspan=2><td class=uk-text-center><td class=uk-text-center><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=23&name=art-table&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTable_Full_Version_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary uk-button-large"target=_blank>Learn More</a></table><h2>Popular Artetics.com Extensions</h2><div class="uk-grid uk-grid-width-large-1-2 uk-grid-width-medium-1-2 uk-grid-width-small-1-1 uk-margin-large"data-uk-grid-margin><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-fast-youtube-logo-600.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Fast Youtube</h3><p>Reduce YouTube video load time by up to 40% over the standard embed code and make your YouTube videos responsive at the same time!<div><a href="https://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=79&name=art-fast-youtube&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTable_Full_Version_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a> <a href="https://www.artetics.com/demo/art-fast-youtube?utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class=uk-button target=_blank>Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-calendar-logo-600-ls.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Calendar</h3><p>Art Calendar is used to create visually rich, interactive, modern calendars that can be quickly deployed using Google Calendar API.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-calendar&cid=1&Itemid=469&category_pathway=19&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTable_Full_Version_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_artcalendar&view=artcalendar&id=1&Itemid=106&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class=uk-button target=_blank>Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-timeline-logo-600-ls.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Timeline</h3><p>Art Timeline enables anyone to build visually rich, timelines. Load events from Admin, Google Drive, Google Calendar or SQL Query.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-timeline&cid=2&Itemid=469&category_pathway=19&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=27&Itemid=130&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class=uk-button target=_blank>Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-data-logo-600-ls.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Data</h3><p>Art Data makes it easy to create 2 types of tables and 12 types of chart and use templates to control the style of your tables and charts.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=7&name=art-data&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/art-data?utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class=uk-button target=_blank>Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-table-logo-600-ls.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Table</h3><p>Art Table is used to insert sortable, searchable tables, multiple types of data charts for easy data presentation from multiple data sources.<div><a href="http://artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-table&cid=23&Itemid=469&category_pathway=19&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=26&Itemid=129&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class=uk-button target=_blank>Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-sexy-lightbox-logo-600-ls.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Sexy Lightbox</h3><p>Art Sexy Lightbox is used for displaying photos, galleries, Imgur, Picasa, Google Photos, Flickr, Photobucket, VirtueMart and more.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=8&name=art-sexy-lightbox&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=21&Itemid=124&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class=uk-button target=_blank>Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-feature-tour-logo-600.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Feature Tour</h3><p>Art Feature Tour is a step by step guide and site introduction tool for Joomla to give a 'tour' of areas of importance to your site.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&product_id=78&name=art-feature-tour&Itemid=469&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a> <a href="http://www.artetics.com/demo/art-feature-tour-illumination?utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class=uk-button target=_blank>Demo</a></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box"><div class=uk-clearfix><div class="uk-margin-right uk-float-left"><img class=uk-margin-right src=../modules/mod_arttable/images/popular/art-adminer-logo-600-ls.jpg style=max-width:140px></div><div class="uk-float-left uk-width-1-2"><h3>Art Adminer</h3><p>Art Adminer is a smart and lightweight database management component and can be used to read, write, alter and many more tasks.<div><a href="http://www.artetics.com/index.php?option=com_hikashop&ctrl=product&task=show&name=art-adminer&cid=58&Itemid=469&category_pathway=24&utm_source=Art_Table_Lite_User_Administrator&utm_medium=display&utm_campaign=ArtTableLite_PopularProducts_Teaser"class="uk-button uk-button-primary"target=_blank>Learn More</a></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></description>
